**story**

Once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who recided on a berry tree which was on a bank of a river.
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife.One day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree the kind hearted offered him some fruits the crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them, as days passed by the crocodile and monkey became good friends.
